  ('dietitian-moex-01907', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-107-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '衛生福利部於101年公告之素食飲食指標，下列建議何者錯誤？', '["多選擇新鮮食材，謹慎選擇加工食品", "富含維生素C蔬果同正餐食用，以改善鐵質吸收率", "建議多攝取菇類、藻類食物，以增加維生素B 之攝取 12", "建議適度日曬10分鐘，以產生充足的活化型態維生素D來幫助鈣質吸收"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0bfeb6891da2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "563ab781ede4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "103", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01908', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-107-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '2025衛生福利政策白皮書，健全青少年健康發展策略中有關飲食之衡量指標不包括下列何者？', '["食鹽", "游離糖", "鈣", "脂肪"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0bfeb6891da2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "563ab781ede4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "103", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
